cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as image description and retrieval based on object-attribute associations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel weakly supervised non-parametric Bayesian model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning). The paper also deals with modeling objects, attributes, and their associations, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing tasks such as image description, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL - Computation and Language). Finally, the paper deals with media sharing sites such as Flickr, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM - Multimedia).
